{
  "stem": "26728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And remember, I was the-- the party of these officers from SHAEF were with these other officers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they were doing was assessing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They very seldom conferred with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With-- We were pretty much on our own, except at-- at billet time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would go back and-- and leave the camp at night, and go to a house where we were billeted, a German house where the families had been evicted, and had our own nice rooms.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They just kicked the people out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, this is what they did, SHAEF.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Eisenhower said, when you're in Germany, you guys sleep in beds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I never slept in Germany, I never slept anyplace except in a nice house on a nice bed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, uh, well, this-- this they didn't disturb, except to turn off the fuel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no gas chamber in-- in Buchenwald, to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The driver, and he and I got to be pretty good buddies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the people that were-- the inmates by now had been told-- they had an organization, by the way, in-- in the camps of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were pretty well organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And um, they had-- they were very, uh, there were some collaborators that were killed, uh, by the inmates.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and uh our troops let it happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were several instances of where the inmates pointed out former SS guards who had changed into, uh, the uniforms of the inmates or raggedy ass clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what-- the way they handled this was they took him into a cell, into the-- the prison section.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made a noose of-- of rope and gave it to the inmate-- to the SS person, told him what to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
